 -- Function: addcol (M, LIST_1, ..., LIST_N)
     Appends the column(s) given by the one or more lists (or matrices)
     onto the matrix _M_.

     See also ‘addrow’ and ‘append’.

     See also: ‘addrow’, ‘append’.


